  {"id": "ex-setslogic-2", "node_id": "sets-logic", "bloom_level": "analyze", "difficulty": 3,
   "type": "single_choice", "stem": "'x²=1'是'x=1'的什么条件？",
   "options": [
     {"label": "A", "text": "充分不必要条件", "is_correct": false},
     {"label": "B", "text": "必要不充分条件", "is_correct": true},
     {"label": "C", "text": "充要条件", "is_correct": false},
     {"label": "D", "text": "既不充分也不必要条件", "is_correct": false, "error_id": "err-sufficient-necessary-reverse"}
   ], "answer": "B",
   "feedback_correct": "正确！x=1⇒x²=1（充分方向成立），但x²=1⇒x=±1不一定x=1（必要方向不成立），所以x²=1是x=1的必要不充分条件。",
   "feedback_wrong": {"A": "方向搞反了。x=1能推出x²=1，所以x²=1是必要条件不是充分条件。", "C": "不是充要的。x²=1时x可能等于-1，不能反推x=1。", "D": "有关系的。x=1⇒x²=1成立，所以x²=1至少是必要条件。"},
   "source": "教材同步", "tags": ["充分必要条件"]},
  {"id": "ex-functions-1", "node_id": "functions-advanced", "bloom_level": "apply", "difficulty": 3,
   "type": "single_choice", "stem": "函数f(x)=log₂(x-1)的定义域是：",
   "options": [
     {"label": "A", "text": "x≥1", "is_correct": false, "error_id": "err-log-domain-equal"},
     {"label": "B", "text": "x>1", "is_correct": true},
     {"label": "C", "text": "x>0", "is_correct": false},
     {"label": "D", "text": "x≥2", "is_correct": false}
   ], "answer": "B",
   "feedback_correct": "正确！对数的真数>0，即x-1>0，解得x>1。",
   "feedback_wrong": {"A": "注意是严格大于！x-1>0不是x-1≥0。当x=1时log₂0无意义。", "C": "需要的是x-1>0不是x>0。", "D": "x-1>0解得x>1，不是x≥2。"},
   "source": "教材同步", "tags": ["函数", "定义域"]},
  {"id": "ex-trig-1", "node_id": "trigonometric-functions", "bloom_level": "apply", "difficulty": 3,
